{"tid":410373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大狗狗疑遭誤認為狼　主人看着被獵殺","createTime":"2017-09-23T00:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T08:12:04.000Z","uid":53379,"like":3,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40e772f5d9502d7b1496eebb74701ba323228df7","tid":410373,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T00:32:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">加拿大狗狗疑遭誤認為狼　主人看着被獵殺</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170922/s00005/937c7cefd8134ea6c130f3f5bc07343d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170922%2Fs00005%2F937c7cefd8134ea6c130f3f5bc07343d.jpg&h=20edc798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖2之2 - 被槍殺的Kaoru。(Canine Valley facebook圖片)<br />\n<br />\n加拿大卑詩省一隻Tamaskan（哈士奇的近親），疑被獵人誤認為狼，於其主人面前被近距離射殺。4歲的Kaoru生前經常到處服務，由自閉症兒童到老人家，Kaoru都能親近。主人對Kaoru的離世感到悲傷，更發起籌款支持反打獵。<br />\n<br />\n卡爾德洛尼（Calderoni）周一（18日）帶同10隻狗隻到惠斯勒附近叢林遠足。當卡爾德洛尼準備為狗隻套上狗繩時，突然聽到一聲巨響，接著看到10英尺外的Kaoru，看著身上的傷口慘叫。卡爾德洛尼立即跑向倒在地上的Kaoru身邊，並輕聲向牠說「離去吧，放心離去吧」。<br />\n<br />\n卑詩省於9月10日起，開放低陸平原地區予獵人殺狼。卑詩省警察指，事件已交由保育主任處理，案件仍在調查中。保育主任亦表示，涉案獵人非常配合調查。<br />\n<br />\n卡爾德洛尼憶述，Kaoru生前最愛園藝，每當她於後院中種樹，如Kaoru對該位置不滿意，都會把小樹連根拔起，再埋到心儀的地方。<br />\n<br />\nKaoru常被主人帶同進行兒童或老人家服務，牠會乖巧地趴在地上，瞇起眼睛，讓自閉症或過度活躍症的小朋友慢慢接近牠。<br />\n<br />\n意外後，卡爾德洛尼已籌得近9000加拿大元(約53000港元)，用作反對當地森林的獵殺狼行動。<br />\n<br />\n(BBC)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170922/s00005/1506063055375\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170922%2Fs00005%2F1506063055375&d=suILLRUCbb1r6ajeQm%2F9vrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=2a9dbe73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170922%2Fs00005%2F1506063055375&h=293ebbeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170922/s00005/1506063055375</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3c951fb6ac057353b04f36ccc9091d901dcdc5","tid":410373,"uid":83882,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T00:36:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n盲西獵人"},{"pid":"f7a253c5287f2b1ac8ca1e4af95bfe4f9a57b78c","tid":410373,"uid":64290,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T00:36:48.000Z","msg":"邊有狼個樣咁on99架<br />\n好慘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686d90be11ef62e3f855a7e070521c3d08d11479","tid":410373,"uid":35749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T00:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d4f0c6e65dc4818b3531685aeb7e4ade3d9030","tid":410373,"uid":79471,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:08:48.000Z","msg":"moonmoon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd06d794c2e10fb00e5ffa6b8a1bec363530b0ab","tid":410373,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e5fbc2bcbb294886e9013f9911e0b8baff1db5","tid":410373,"uid":148365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:18:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\